Urkal tried in vain to even match his Cuban rival, only
managed to avoid a knockout defeat.
</P>
<P>
With three categories remaining in the Olympic boxing
tournament, Cuba has one more shot at gold medal as Alfredo
Duvergel takes on David Reid of the United States in the 71kg
final.
</P>
<P>
The two beaten semi-finalist Fathi Missaoui of Tunisia and
Bolat Niyazymbetov of Kazakhstan finished third in the 63.5kg
class. 
