<HEADLINE> Ireland to Accord Olympic Heroine with Red-Carpet Welcome </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, August 5 (Xinhua) -- Ireland will roll out red carpet
to greet its Olympic heroine Michelle Smith returning from Atlanta
on Tuesday, according to reports from Dublin.
</P>
<P>
President Mary Robinson will greet triple gold medalist Smith
and the rest of the Irish team at Dublin airport before an
open-topped bus cavalcade drives into the city center for a mass
rally.
