as the centennial Olympic Games ended in Atlanta, Georgia of the
United States on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Kenya Times
</P>
<P>
-- Kenyan ruling KANU's headquarters on Sunday said threats to
boycott next year's polls by the opposition will not intimidate
the party's "great march" to the 1997 general elections. 
