Friday and Sunday as 20 million cars and trucks took to the roads,
leading to traffic jams and tailbacks of up to 10 kilometers in
some areas of southern Italy.
</P>
<P>
Police have been put on high alert to cope with the mass exodus
from cities to holiday destinations. 
